  "title": "Finance Executive (AR)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a market leader in Logistics industry. They are looking for a Finance Executive (AR) to assist the team for the next phrase of their business. They are located at West of Singapore– easily accessible. The Finance Executive is responsible for:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Duties</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>AR Management &amp; Collections</strong> – Reduce AR aging, optimise collections, and manage daily collection activities, including liaising with customers and internal stakeholders.</li>\n  <li><strong>Invoicing &amp; Statements</strong> – Prepare and issue sales invoices, debit notes, and statements of accounts to customers.</li>\n  <li><strong>Financial Reporting &amp; Month-End Closing</strong> – Assist in journal preparation, balance sheet schedules, and follow up on outstanding items for month-end closing.</li>\n  <li><strong>Reconciliation &amp; Audit Support</strong> – Reconcile inter-company balances, bank items, and other financial records to ensure accuracy.</li>\n  <li><strong>Collaboration &amp; Process Improvement</strong> – Work with internal stakeholders to enhance AR processes, operational efficiency, and participate in digitalisation or system enhancement projects.</li>\n  <li><strong>Ad-Hoc Duties</strong> – Perform other assigned tasks as required to support the finance and business units.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Accounting and Finance or equivalent with 2 years of experience</li>\n  <li>Experience in Microsoft Office and Accounting ERP such as SAP Hana</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9682</p>\n<p>EA Reg. No. R23115141 (Tan Su Yee)</p>",
